trans-unit.target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05006_000001_OLDTITANIA<tab>Who goes there? Are you the one who broke the seal?
TEXT_VOICEMAN_05006_000002_OLDTITANIA<tab>Ah, so much time lost... So much frolicking and feasting left undone...
TEXT_VOICEMAN_05006_000003_OLDTITANIA<tab>We must make up for it, we must... Beginning by playing with <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var>!
TEXT_VOICEMAN_05006_000110_VAUTHRY<tab>Are you so determined to die? One last chance, villains: bow down and acknowledge your king. Your god!
TEXT_VOICEMAN_05006_000210_EMETSELCH<tab>Show me your “vaunted” strength. And I shall expose the lie of your fragmented existence!
